page.title: 11Homelife
page.content: When we get out of school at ten to four,we usually change and then go out to play.Three nights a week there are some clubs,which some of us go to.On a Saturday we play outside most of the day.Sometimes your mum or dad will take you to the swimming pool in Portree.On week days we usually go to bed at about eight or nine o clock. On Friday some childern stay up quite late because there is no school the next day.On Sundays most of us go to church.On Sunday night we have to go to bed early so that we can get up early for school next morning.
